{"tid":890202,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"浸大(中國)內地生：失意高考遇港校宣傳","createTime":"2018-11-05T06:45:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T06:50:31.000Z","uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b4e942f467e60257ce7dd50fbe29f032a695b9df","tid":890202,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:45:46.000Z","msg":"浸大(中國)內地生：失意高考遇港校宣傳<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】八大部分學士課程的(中國)內地生佔非本地生比例仍然偏高，其中有大學更佔逾九成。現時在浸會大學計算機科學系就讀2年級、來自(中國)內地吉林省的李同學表示，因在(中國)內地的高考成績未能升上心儀大學，故報考香港的大學一試。<br />\n<br />\n(中國)內地的頂尖大學分為「985院校」及「211院校」，當中以985院校更為優秀，(中國)全國有約39間院校包括北京大學及清華大學為985院校。<br />\n<br />\n感港生自視過高<br />\n<br />\n李同學說原想考上屬985院校的(中國)華中科技大學，不過高考成績未如理想，要考上心儀大學「有點勉強」。她說讀高中時，香港有不同大學曾到其學校宣傳，其中包括浸會大學；她以高考成績報讀數間本地大學，最終獲浸大取錄。<br />\n<br />\n「知名度高 自然多海外生」<br />\n<br />\n浸大現時共有約767名(中國)內地生就讀全日制學士課程，佔非本地生人數88%，為八大中第二高；最高是教育大學。<br />\n<br />\n李同學來港2年，她說無論生活及讀書上均能適應，亦能跟上英文進度。被問如何看待評價本地大學非本地生中，(中國)內地生佔大多數，李不諱言，「如（相關）大學的知名度較高，自然有多點<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">海外生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong>報讀」。<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>她又表示有感香港大學生有時「自視過高」，指(中國)內地在許多方面如科技發展已超過香港，認為本地生應謙虛學習。</strong></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6e971925f692f0773284068c27e57d26ccc9bd47","tid":890202,"uid":53026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://9.blog.xuite.net/9/1/0/7/23348663/blog_1910721/txt/63874287/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9.blog.xuite.net%2F9%2F1%2F0%2F7%2F23348663%2Fblog_1910721%2Ftxt%2F63874287%2F1.jpg&h=83624731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應謙虛學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9508d8192817898608e290777a878019b67b7af","tid":890202,"uid":169116,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:48:57.000Z","msg":"舉報佢呢個分裂國家領土嘅港獨份子啦"},{"pid":"b64f660dfa1631f7ee8d74a9f2b880b988e21958","tid":890202,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:49:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a91bd0a34ff312883ce5237b494e1f823e1492f7","tid":890202,"uid":4964,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6e971925f692f0773284068c27e57d26ccc9bd47","tid":890202,"uid":53026,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://9.blog.xuite.net/9/1/0/7/23348663/blog_1910721/txt/63874287/1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F9.blog.xuite.net%2F9%2F1%2F0%2F7%2F23348663%2Fblog_1910721%2Ftxt%2F63874287%2F1.jpg&h=83624731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應謙虛學習<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:50:08.000Z","msg":"個時沈祖堯就威呀,個中國人收香港人全額獎學金鬧香港人係狗都冇事,仲叫香港人包容<br />\n新加坡發生同樣事件即刻停學趕出境"},{"pid":"156ad1dc9fd859ec2d8d0b2de708841e6532c8cd","tid":890202,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T06:50:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}